現機械臂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nT-Mobile最終不准任何華為員工入內」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"隻機械臂自己爬左入去個袋度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92869a84b3d93fbfaa3f1f28c4880e6fc5d0a23f","tid":1001661,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019b7144147665670c285d32ba857c70a4f6f610","tid":1001661,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b68c66fdca38e45763e53863d2d92a3d7897c85","tid":1001661,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60bfcab7c55448e077bb8db8dd6a3d69863c5a96","tid":1001661,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"連犯三次仲比佢入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係保密協議唔洗佢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"第三次斷正之後唔俾入喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「最初否認但其後指在袋中發現機械臂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nT-Mobile最終不准任何華為員工入內」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"隻機械臂自己爬左入去個袋度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"咁似講緊套動畫mechanical arms<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393e49bec88fe4672d983184b897359f6f284d91","tid":1001661,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92869a84b3d93fbfaa3f1f28c4880e6fc5d0a23f","tid":1001661,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019b7144147665670c285d32ba857c70a4f6f610","tid":1001661,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b68c66fdca38e45763e53863d2d92a3d7897c85","tid":1001661,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"第三次斷正之後唔俾入喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.